      • TPC_HPAY_DEVICE_INFO_ERROR

        public static final TPCSDKExceptionType TPC_HPAY_DEVICE_INFO_ERROR
        This error is thrown when there's an error upon retrieving a device info from Huawei Pay Wallet. It could happen when one of these following condition are meet:

        • The user does not agree to the wallet agreement
        • The network is unavailable
        • The user has not logged in to the Huawei Wallet
        • The current country or region does not have the bank card service. The device information cannot be obtained
        • Failed to get openDeviceID from server

        Please check the logs for more details and contact our support team.
